<br>
As such, a 200k hp mob with a high dmg AE and you're only allowed to bring 18-24 people to fight it, I could see where SoS would be better than GSS.  You are looking for SPEED, not Endurance.  Go in with Spellshield, Epic both up, and you can easily dump your mana and do 12-15k in about 30 seconds before the recourse seriously hurts you.  At 1k mana, I could probably get 5, maybe 6 off with focus and spec factored in.  That's 1800 hp, minus the 1500 from epic and Spellshield, so that's a grand total of 300 hp.  I'm fairly sure I can handle that.<br>
<br>
Who knows, SoS may suck complete and total ass.  I'm just not going to judge it too harshly till PoP is released. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=74028"target=new>Neuro the Strategist</a><BR>
